<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Asian Water Monitor</title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" />

  <style>
    :root{
      --navbar-offset:70px;
      --monitor-img-w:360px;
      --section-gap:384px;
      --green:#1DB954;              /* brighter green */
      --glass: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
      --stroke: rgba(255,255,255,0.14);
    }

    html, body { height:100%; }
    body{
      background:#000;
      color:var(--green);
      margin:0;
      min-height:100vh;
      display:flex;
      flex-direction:column;
      padding-top:var(--navbar-offset);
      font-family:Arial, sans-serif;
    }

    .page-content{ flex:1; }

    h1, h2, h3, p, li, strong{ color:var(--green); }

    /* Extra spacing under navbar for title */
    .page-title {
      margin-top: 30px;   /* creates the gap */
      text-align: center;
      color: var(--green);
    }

    .asian-monitor-img{
      width:var(--monitor-img-w);
      max-width:100%;
      height:auto;
      display:block;
      margin:0 auto 1rem;
      border-radius:10px;
      box-shadow:0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.7);
    }

    .price-tag{
      font-size:1.75rem;
      font-weight:800;
      letter-spacing:.5px;
      text-align:center;
      margin-bottom:1.5rem;
      color:var(--green);
    }

    .care-card{
      background:var(--glass);
      border:1px solid var(--stroke);
      border-radius:16px;
      padding:1.25rem;
    }
    .care-card h2{
      font-size:1.25rem;
      margin-bottom:.75rem;
      text-transform:uppercase;
      letter-spacing:.06em;
      color:var(--green);
    }
    .care-grid{
      display:grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap:1rem;
    }
    @media (min-width: 768px){
      .care-grid{ grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr; }
    }
    .care-box{
      background:rgba(0,0,0,0.35);
      border:1px solid var(--stroke);
      border-radius:12px;
      padding:1rem;
      height:100%;
    }
    .care-box h3{ font-size:1.05rem; margin-bottom:.5rem; color:var(--green); }
    .care-box ul{ margin:0; padding-left:1.1rem; }
    .care-box li{ color:var(--green); }

    .care-note{
      font-size:.95rem;
      margin-top:1rem;
      color:var(--green);
    }

    .monitor-section{ margin-bottom:var(--section-gap); }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <%- include('partials/navbar') %>

  <main class="page-content">
    <div class="container py-5 monitor-section">
      <!-- Title -->
      <h1 class="page-title mb-4">Asian Water Monitor</h1>

      <!-- Image -->
      <div class="text-center">
        <img
          src="/Images/inventory_image_Asian water_monitor.png"
          alt="Asian Water Monitor"
          class="asian-monitor-img"
        />
      </div>

      <!-- Price -->
      <div class="price-tag">$350</div>

      <!-- Care Guide -->
      <section class="care-card">
        <h2>Care Guide (Quick Reference)</h2>

        <div class="care-grid">
          <!-- BABY -->
          <div class="care-box">
            <h3>Baby (Hatchling – ~10–14&quot;)</h3>
            <ul>
              <li><strong>Enclosure (min):</strong> 36&quot; × 18&quot; × 16&quot; (~40 gal) with a swim pan.</li>
              <li><strong>Humidity:</strong> 60–70%.</li>
              <li><strong>Temps:</strong> Ambient mid-80s °F; <strong>bask</strong> 120–140 °F.</li>
              <li><strong>UVB/Light:</strong> High-output T5 UVB or metal-halide; provide full-body bask zone.</li>
              <li><strong>Feeding:</strong> Daily to every other day; gut-loaded insects (roaches/crickets), occasional fish; small rodents sparingly; dust Ca+D3 as advised.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <!-- JUVENILE -->
          <div class="care-box">
            <h3>Juvenile (~3–4 ft)</h3>
            <ul>
              <li><strong>Enclosure (min):</strong> ~4' × 4' × 4' (larger is better); climbing + large water tub.</li>
              <li><strong>Humidity:</strong> 60–70%.</li>
              <li><strong>Temps:</strong> Ambient mid-80s °F; <strong>bask</strong> 125–140 °F.</li>
              <li><strong>UVB/Light:</strong> Strong UVB; follow lamp UVI guidance; provide shade options.</li>
              <li><strong>Feeding:</strong> 3–4×/week; insects, rodents, fish/eggs; avoid obesity.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <!-- ADULT -->
          <div class="care-box">
            <h3>Adult (5–8+ ft typical)</h3>
            <ul>
              <li><strong>Enclosure (min):</strong> ~8' × 6' × 8' (room size better); deep water feature.</li>
              <li><strong>Humidity:</strong> 60–70%; ensure ventilation.</li>
              <li><strong>Temps:</strong> Ambient mid-80s °F; <strong>bask</strong> 125–140 °F; allow cool retreat.</li>
              <li><strong>UVB/Light:</strong> Full-spectrum with strong UVB; follow manufacturer distance charts.</li>
              <li><strong>Feeding:</strong> 2–3×/week; whole-prey focus (rodents, fish, eggs); rotate items.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <p class="care-note">
          <strong>Heating & Lamp Distance:</strong> Use a temp gun to set basking surface at 120–140 °F. As a <em>starting point</em>, many 150 W ceramic heat emitters and flood lamps end up ~12–18&quot; above the basking spot in tall enclosures. Never place heat lamps closer than ~12&quot; (≈30 cm). Adjust height/wattage to hit temps safely.<br><br>
          <strong>Nighttime:</strong> Provide a heat source that does not emit light (e.g., ceramic emitters or radiant heat panels). Ambient should not drop below ~75 °F.<br><br>
          <strong>Exercise & Enrichment:</strong> Asian Water Monitors are highly active and intelligent. Provide climbing branches, swimming space, and interaction to prevent stress and obesity.
        </p>
      </section>

      <!-- Back Button -->
      <div class="text-center mt-4">
        <a href="/monitor_lizard_inventory" class="btn btn-success btn-lg">Back to Inventory</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <%- include('partials/footer') %>

  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
